### Polymarket Position API Testing

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@walletAddress = 0xfa68d87db6ca75a31baba74ab8259fd4728ff3ba

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get all positions for a wallet
GET {{baseUrl}}/positions/{{walletAddress}}

### Get position value for a wallet
GET {{baseUrl}}/positions/{{walletAddress}}/value

### Close a position (sell all shares)
POST {{baseUrl}}/positions/{{walletAddress}}/close?market_id=0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678&outcome=YES

### Close a position (sell specific amount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/positions/{{walletAddress}}/close?market_id=0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678&outcome=NO&amount=100.5

### Example with real wallet address (replace with actual address)
# GET {{baseUrl}}/positions/0xYourWalletAddressHere

